snippet.title: METEORA Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Race for survival as a meteor in a young, chaotic universe in Big Boot Games' award winning arcade combat racer METEORA, launching on PC July 14th 2022

Play the Demo and Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1155220/METEORA/
